definition:
Someone descended from Jamin who was a man of the tribe of Simeon living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, first mentioned at Gen.46.10; 
 son of: Simeon (H8095); 
 brother of: Jemuel (H3223), Ohad (H0161), Jachin (H3199), Zerah (H2226L) and Shaul (H7586H)
Group of ya.min (יָמִין "Jamin" H3226)
 § Jaminites , of Jamin "the right hand"
 the descendants of Jamin
